#N canvas 190 33 1280 800 12;
#X text 30 14 ns_alien_evo3 — minimal corpus-based pipeline (mutate-only);
#X text 30 32 ───────────────────────────────────────────────;
#X text 30 50 ns_corpus owns the parent pool with quality+novelty admission. The seed bank;
#X text 30 64 from seeds.txt is loaded as protected entries on loadbang. Each tick samples;
#X text 30 78 a parent from the corpus \, mutates via ns_seq_propose \, evaluates via [alien] \,;
#X text 30 92 scores both novelty (ns_archive) and quality (ns_quality) \, and admits if both;
#X text 30 106 thresholds pass. Every admitted child becomes a future parent.;
#X text 30 124 Click [seeds( first to load \, then toggle the metro to evolve.;
